<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A directional light is a light source that behaves similar to sunlight. The light from a directional light hits all objects from the same direction and with the same intensity, regardless of where they are in the scene.</db:para>
</db:section>
